:"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>SyntaxError</strong></code>&nbsp;对象代表尝试解析语法上不合法的代码的错误。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>当 Javascript 语言解析代码时，JavaScript 引擎发现了不符合语法规范的 tokens 或 token 顺序时抛出<code>SyntaxError</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>new SyntaxError([<var>message</var>[, <var>fileName</var>[, <var>lineNumber</var>]]])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"message\"><code>message</code></dt>\n <dd>可选的。可阅读的错误描述信息</dd>\n <dt id=\"filename\"><code>fileName</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>可选的。包含引发异常的代码的文件名</dd>\n <dt id=\"linenumber\"><code>lineNumber</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>可选的。包含引发异常的代码的行号</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"syntaxerror.prototype_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/SyntaxError\"><code>SyntaxError.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>允许 <code>SyntaxError</code>对象添加属性。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p>全局 <code>SyntaxError</code>&nbsp;自身不包含任何方法，但从原型链中继承了一些方法。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntaxerror_instances","title":"<code>SyntaxError</code>&nbsp;实例","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"SyntaxError 实例"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties_of_syntaxerror_instances","title":"属性","isH3":true,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">{{page('/zh-CN/do